<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٤٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٥٠٦٠ -<span class="c5"> عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ:</span> أَخْبَرَنَا مَعْمَرٌ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ الْحَسَنِ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«إِذَا اخْتَلَفَ الرَّاهِنُ وَالْمُرْتَهِنُ، فَالْقَوْلُ قَوْلُ الرَّاهِنِ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>